title: The Computers are Coming!
description:
The Computer are Coming!


An enjoyable little book by Dr. David F. Webber, a pastor at the Southwest Radio Church, Oklahoma City, Oklahoma.

This book was written in 1978 (updated 1980) and predicts how the world will end by the year 2000 and revelations is being fulfilled because of the coming of the digital age.

The book is filled with both religious and science articles all showing the concern with the coming digital age ALL OF WHICH has been shown to be inaccurate. Please do not post about how Christianly is evil, I really don't care.

This is for educational and historical purposes only, it's just a fun book on how some people in 1978 saw the future.

Enjoy.
